ionservice`\n   - `recommendationservice` 的内部处理延迟增加表明其自身也存在性能问题\n\n4. **调用关系**：\n   - 拓扑结构显示：Frontend → Recommendation → ProductCatalog 的调用路径存在异常\n   - ProductCatalog 服务是多个依赖链的公共下游，可能是系统瓶颈", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的指标数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。从数据中可以看出，故障期间出现了多个Pod的指标异常。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"pod_cpu_usage\", \"pod_network_receive_packets\", \"pod_network_transmit_packets\", \"pod_processes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes指标从1.0降至0.0，表明Pod进程终止或重启，同时pod_cpu_usage也出现异常变化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes: 1.0→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0), pod_cpu_usage: 0.0→0.0 (change_ratio=0.0)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage和网络包传输指标显著下降，可能受到redis-cart-0故障的连锁影响\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.04→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0), pod_network_transmit_packets: 106.86→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage和网络包传输指标异常下降，与前端服务整体异常一致\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.04→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0), pod_network_transmit_packets: 98.72→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage和网络包传输指标异常下降，前端服务集群普遍受影响\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.04→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0), pod_network_transmit_packets: 90.71→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage和网络包传输/接收指标显著下降，可能因redis-cart-0故障导致依赖服务异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.06→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0), pod_network_transmit_packets: 287.29→0.0 (change_ratio=2.0)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点总结：**\n\n1. **核心发现**：`redis-cart-0` Pod的`pod_processes`指标从1.0降至0.0，这是最关键的故障信号，表明该Pod可能发生了重启或崩溃。\n\n2. **影响范围**：多个前端服务Pod（frontend-0,1,2）和产品目录服务Pod（productcatalogservice-2）的CPU使用率和网络包传输指标均降为0，显示出明显的服务中断。\n\n3. **故障模式**：从指标变化模式看，这更像是一个级联故障，`redi